	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The most recent project I am working on has a workable demo that I just released today! It's a dungeon crawler style game.<br /><br />I'll just copy/paste what I posted on NintendoAge:<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Following up with the E3 video we put out (view <a href="http://slydogstudios.org/index.php/2013/06/sly-dog-studios-e3-2013/" class="postlink">here</a> or <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LJHsj9AH9Ys" class="postlink">here</a>), Sly Dog Studios is now putting out the demo for Candelabra: Estoscerro!<br /><br />To download the zip file, go here:<br /><br /><a href="http://slydogstudios.org/index.php/2013/06/candelabra-estoscerro-demo-release/" class="postlink">http://slydogstudios.org/index.php/2013/06/candelabra-estoscerro-demo-release/</a><br /><br />The controls present a bit of a learning curve at first, but I think you'll find it feels somewhat natural after giving it a bit o' time. Screenshot!<br /><br /><img src="http://slydogstudios.org/images/candelabra_demo_screenshot.png" alt="Image" /><br /><br />Go, download, enjoy!</div><br /><br />And that be it!

		

